container.value:
CITTADELLE AISHO KASUGAI 302,
Rokkenya-cho 1-150, Kasugai, Aichi,
486-0842, JAPAN

creator: Indigo Software
descriptionHtml:
In the Health Log, the current weight, muscle mass, body temperature, blood pressure, oxygen concentration, exercise amount, etc. are visualized in a list display and a graph display.

It's easy and simple, so you can keep going every day.

Items that can be managed are :
- body weight
- body fat percentage
- BMI (automatic calculation)
- Muscle mass
- Body temperature
- blood pressure
- Pulse rate
- Oxygen concentration
- Training amount
- Calories burned
You can manage morning and night data.
Body temperature can be managed up to two digits after the decimal point according to the basal body temperature.

Each
·graph
·list
It can also be displayed in.

Training amount and calories burned can be linked with "Exercise Walking":
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jimdo.uchida001tmhr.stepcounter

You can also start :
Medication management app "Medication Schedule 2"
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jimdo.uchida001tmhr.medicineschedule2
and
Meal photo management app "Meal Photo"
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jimdo.uchida001tmhr.mealrec

There is a function to print the data or report it as a CSV file.
A plug-in is required for printing.

EPSON (operation confirmed):
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.epson.mobilephone.android.epsonprintserviceplugin
Canon:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.canon.android.printservice.plugin

For statistical information, you can also get the average of standard weight, weight difference to the target weight, 1 week, 2 weeks, 1 month, 2 months, 3 months, 6 months.

Theme color
- White
- Sky blue
- Green
- Yellow
- Orange
- Pink
You can choose from.

It also has a data export / import function that can be used for model changes.

You can manage the data of multiple people. (in-app purchase needed)
